# - LOCAL DEVELOPMENT: Use local Supabase (Docker-based PostgreSQL)
# - PRODUCTION: Use remote Supabase (hosted on supabase.co)
#
# Copy this file to:
# - .env.local (for local development) - preferred for dev work
# - .env.development (for production) - keep your production credentials here
# ============================================================================

